---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageHero from "../../components/PageHero";
import schoolGroupImg from "../../assets/images/Community/school-group.webp";
import libraryBalloonsImg from "../../assets/images/Community/library-balloons.webp";
import playgroundFunImg from "../../assets/images/Community/playground-fun.webp";

const article = {
    title: "Tourism that Heals",
    subtitle: "Beyond the Transaction",
    heroImage: schoolGroupImg.src,
    date: "January 10, 2026",
    author: "Marga Team",
    readTime: "3 min read",
};
---

<Layout
    title={article.title}
    description="Discover how your journey puts roofs over heads and books in hands. A look into our 'Sharing Warmth' initiative in the remote villages of Nepal."
    image={article.heroImage}
>
    <PageHero
        title="Beyond Tourism"
        subtitle="When you travel with heart, you leave more than footprints."
        image={article.heroImage}
        parallax={true}
    />

    <article class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            {/* Header Info */}
            <div
                class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-100 pb-8 mb-12"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gray-100 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center border border-gray-100"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/logo.webp"
                            alt="Marga Team"
                            class="w-8 h-8 object-contain"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <p
                            class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-900"
                        >
                            {article.author}
                        </p>
                        <p
                            class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1"
                        >
                            Community Initiative
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-right">
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-900">
                        {article.date}
                    </p>
                    <p
                        class="text-[10px] text-brand uppercase tracking-widest mt-1"
                    >
                        {article.readTime}
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            {/* Content */}
            <div
                class="prose prose-lg prose-headings:font-serif prose-headings:font-bold prose-headings:text-gray-900 prose-p:text-gray-800 prose-blockquote:font-serif prose-blockquote:text-brand-dark prose-blockquote:not-italic prose-blockquote:border-brand max-w-none leading-loose"
            >
                <p
                    class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-900 font-serif italic mb-10 leading-relaxed border-l-4 border-brand pl-8 py-2"
                >
                    "We often ask what we can get from a destination. But the
                    most profound travel experiences happen when we ask: what
                    can we give?"
                </p>

                <p
                    class="mb-8 first-letter:text-7xl first-letter:font-bold first-letter:text-brand first-letter:float-left first-letter:mr-4 first-letter:mt-[-10px]"
                >
                    In the high villages of Ruby Valley, the winter wind bites
                    hard. It finds the gaps in the stone walls; it creeps under
                    thin blankets. For many years, we walked through these
                    villages as trekkers, admirers of the landscape. We took our
                    photos of the snow-capped peaks and the smiling children.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-8">
                    But one day, we stopped just looking. We started <em
                        >seeing</em
                    >. We saw that behind the beautiful smiles, there were
                    shivering hands. We saw that the "rustic charm" of a school
                    often meant a roof that leaked icy water onto textbooks.
                </p>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">
                    The Birth of 'Sharing Warmth'
                </h3>
                <p class="mb-8">
                    We realized that Marga Adventure could not just be a tour
                    company. We had to be a bridge. A bridge between the
                    resources of our guests and the needs of our hosts.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-8">
                    This is not "charity" in the cold, distant sense. This is
                    family. When you Trek with us, a portion of your fee goes
                    directly into the <strong>Sharing Warmth</strong> fund. But more
                    than that, we invite you to be part of the distribution.
                </p>

                <div class="my-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <div class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden h-[300px]">
                        <img
                            src={libraryBalloonsImg.src}
                            alt="Children with balloons"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
                            loading="lazy"
                            decoding="async"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden h-[300px]">
                        <img
                            src={playgroundFunImg.src}
                            alt="Playground Fun"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
                            loading="lazy"
                            decoding="async"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            {/* Footer Nav */}
            <div
                class="mt-24 pt-12 border-t border-gray-100 flex justify-between items-center"
            >
                <a
                    href="/blog/philosophy-of-silence"
                    class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 hover:text-brand transition-colors"
                    >← Previous</a
                >
                <a
                    href="/blog"
                    class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 hover:text-brand transition-colors"
                    >Back to Journal</a
                >
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
</Layout>
